What is the output of the following code? 
 int x = 10; 
 int y = x++; 
 std::cout << y << std::endl;

What is the output of the following code? 
 int arr[] = {1, 2, 3}; 
 int* ptr = arr; 
 std::cout << *++ptr << std::endl;

What is the output of the following code? 
 int x = 10; 
 int y = 20; 
 int* ptr1 = &x; 
 int* ptr2 = &y; 
 std::cout << *ptr1 + *ptr2 << std::endl;

What is the output of the following code? 
 int arr[] = {1, 2, 3, 4}; 
 std::cout << arr << std::endl;
